com.interpss.core.acsc
Interface AcscBus

All Superinterfaces:
AclfBus, Bus, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ExtensionElement, IAclfBus, IAclfBusAdaptation, IAclfBusAdjustment, IAclfBusFunc, IAcscBus, IAdaptable, IBusSwitchBreakModel, NameTag, NetworkedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
AcscBusImpl
public interface AcscBus
extends AclfBus, IAcscBus

A representation of the model object 'Bus'. * Notes 1) for NotContribute bus, z1,z2=Zload, z0=Zload if grounded. * only SolidGround and Ungrounded allowd for groundType * * --- --- --- --- * | | | | * z1 z2 z0 z0 * | | | | * - - - * SolidG UnG * * 2) for Contributing bus, z1=x1, z2=x2, z0=x0+3*GX_R if grounded. * * --- --- --- --- * | | | | * E --z1--| z2 z0+3*GX_R z0 z0 * | | | | * - - - * ZG SolidG UnG * * E could be 1.0/0deg or use LF voltage to calculate AcscBus could be extended using IAascBus interface

The following features are supported:

  • Sc Code
  • Sc Z1
  • Sc Z2
  • Sc Z0
  • Grounding
